<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Bill</ENAMEX>/<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Payment Mail</ENAMEX>


•
<ENAMEX TYPE="CONTACT_INFO">Household bill/</ENAMEX>payment mail, as defined in this analysis,
