•
So far, however, the number of bill/payment pieces lost
is too small to have any material impact on <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">First-Class</ENAMEX> volume.
Payment mail is declining fast while bill mail is still increasing,
though at a falling rate. <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">Between 1990 and 1997</TIMEX>, the number of
