pieces in <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">seven years</TIMEX>.


•
So far, it seems that <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">households</ENAMEX> are converting from
paying by mail to other methods of payment at a faster rate than
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">businesses</ENAMEX> are converting their methods of sending bills.
