<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Household Diary Study</ENAMEX>
All data used in this analysis come from a market research study
called the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Household Diary Study</ENAMEX> (HDS). Thus, before we turn to the
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">data</ENAMEX>, I would like to review some highlights related to this
study.
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">HDS</ENAMEX> is financed by the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Postal Service</ENAMEX> and is conducted annually
by <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Chilton Research Services</ENAMEX>, a market research <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">firm</ENAMEX> located in
