the <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">years between 1977 and 1987</TIMEX> for <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">annual</TIMEX> comparisons.
HDS collects information on household mail by surveying a random
sample of <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">5,300</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">households</ENAMEX> per year. Each <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">household</ENAMEX> is surveyed for
